# Cursor Rules for CEO of One

## Project Context
This is the CEO of One website - an AI-powered chief of staff for solo CEOs. Part of the Utlyze "Of One" suite targeting solo professionals.

## Key Guidelines
- Follow Utlyze brand guidelines: clean minimalist design
- Primary color: #4169E1 (Utlyze blue)
- Accent color: #FF6B35 (Orange for CTAs)
- Target audience: Solo CEOs drowning in the 80% that doesn't matter
- Core message: Focus on critical 20%, AI handles the rest

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Next.js 14 with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Express.js with TypeScript
- Database: Supabase
- Deployment: Vercel

## Agent Tasks
When working as a background agent, check the current task and focus only on that specific deliverable.